---
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
import hero from "../../public/img/hero.svg";
---

<section>
    <div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-2xl sm:px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 lg:py-24">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center mx-auto max-w-7xl">
            <div class="mt-16 w-full lg:max-w-lg lg:w-1/2 rounded-xl lg:mt-0">
                <div>
                    <div class="relative w-full max-w-lg">
                        <div
                            class="absolute top-0 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 -right-4  w-56 h-56 mix-blend-lighten filter blur-[75px] opacity-70 animate-blob"
                        >
                        </div>

                        <div
                            class="absolute rounded-full bg-emerald-400 -bottom-8 right-28 w-56 h-56 mix-blend-lighten filter blur-[75px] opacity-70 animate-blob animation-delay-4000"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <Image class="drop-shadow-sm" src={hero} alt="hero"/>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div
                class="flex flex-col items-start mt-12 text-left lg:flex-grow lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-6 xl:pl-24 md:mb-0 xl:mt-0"
            >
                <span class="mb-8 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-blue-500 uppercase lg:mt-20">
                    Inspira, Conecta, Destaca
                </span>
                <h1
                    class="mb-8 text-4xl font-bold leading-none tracking-tighter text-white md:text-7xl lg:text-5xl"
                >
                    ¡Tu Página Web, Tu Estilo, Nuestro Arte!
                </h1>
                <p class="mb-8 text-base leading-relaxed text-left text-gray-400">
                    Explora cómo nuestro enfoque personalizado y experiencia en desarrollo web pueden llevar tu negocio al siguiente nivel.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>